	&lt;li&gt;Copyright Law of the United States of America, § 105. Subject matter of copyright: United States Government works: &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.copyright.gov/title17/92chap1.html#105&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;http://www.copyright.gov/title17/92chap1.html#105&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
